sequenceDiagram
    participant U as User
    participant G as Group Owner
    participant A as Admin
    participant API as Analytics API
    participant CACHE as Redis Cache
    participant DB as MongoDB
    participant JOB as BullMQ Jobs

    %% User Analytics Flow
    U->>API: GET /analytics/user/my/overview
    API->>CACHE: Check cache
    CACHE-->>API: Miss
    API->>DB: Aggregate user tasks
    DB-->>API: Task data
    API->>API: Calculate streak & score
    API->>CACHE: Cache results (5m)
    API-->>U: Analytics data

    %% Group Analytics Flow
    G->>API: GET /analytics/group/:id/overview
    API->>CACHE: Check cache
    CACHE-->>API: Miss
    API->>DB: Aggregate group data
    DB-->>API: Group + member data
    API->>API: Calculate leaderboard
    API->>CACHE: Cache results (5m)
    API-->>G: Group analytics

    %% Admin Analytics Flow
    A->>API: GET /analytics/admin/dashboard
    API->>CACHE: Check cache
    CACHE-->>API: Miss
    API->>DB: Aggregate platform data
    DB-->>API: Platform metrics
    API->>API: Calculate growth & revenue
    API->>CACHE: Cache dashboard (10m)
    API-->>A: Complete dashboard

    %% Background Job Flow
    JOB->>DB: Pre-compute daily stats
    DB-->>JOB: Aggregated data
    JOB->>CACHE: Update cache
    CACHE-->>JOB: Cached
    Note over JOB: Runs at midnight daily
